snippet.title: Purple Chicken Spaceman Release Trailer
snippet.description:
*Hey everyone! Turn on Captions for Sing-Along Mode!*

Our latest shenanigans are taking the form of a game called Purple Chicken Spaceman, coming to your Xbox One on May the 3rd, 2019!  Pre-orders are available April 26th, but for now enjoy the catchy earworm that Parry Gripp created exclusively for this silly project!

Game description: From the creators of Hurdle Turtle comes this zany, tough-as-nails cartoon 2D Space Shooter featuring all-new tracks by the internet's own Parry Gripp (Nerf Herder)!

More info: http://bit.ly/PCHICKEN
Official Facebook Page: http://bit.ly/PCHICKENFB
